92, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 4, "EnglishDescription": "The Camels fore limbs should be tied till the thighs. A person should stand on the right side and strike a spear, knife or a dagger on its neck deeply. The camel is sacrificed standing.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Agar Oont ki qurbaani kar rahe hai to usey khada kar ke naher karna chahiye. Dono agle (front) paiyr ghootno tak baandhe aur daaheni taraf khade ho kar gardan ke neechle hisse par chaaku (knife), nezeh ya khanjar bhonk de.", "UrduDescription": "اگر اونٹ کی قربانی کر رہا ہے تو اسے کھڑا کرکے نحر کرنا چاہیئے، دونوں اگلے پیر گھٹنوں تک باندھے اور داہنی طرف کھڑے ہو کر گردن کے نچلے حصہ پر چاقو، نیزہ یا خنجر بھونک دے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "Arabic